>\n* [[Adi Nes]], Israeli photographer.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.adines.com/content/gay%20and%20lesbian%20TIMES%20-%20Myth,%20militarism%20and%20gay%20identity.htm | title=Myth, militarism and gay identity}}</ref>\n*[[Arnold Scaasi]], Canadian-born American fashion designer<ref>{{cite web|last=St |first=James |url=http://worldofwonder.net/2011/08/02/Arnold_Scassi_and_Parker_Ladd_ma/ |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130413214824/http://worldofwonder.net/2011/08/02/Arnold_Scassi_and_Parker_Ladd_ma/ |url-status=dead |archive-date=2013-04-13 |title=True Love Tuesdays: Arnold Scaasi and Parker Ladd's love story |publisher=Worldofwonder.net |date=2011-08-02 |accessdate=2013-11-19 }}</ref>\n*[[Isaac Mizrahi]], American fashion designer<ref>{{cite web|last=Krupnick |first=Eilie|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/01/05/isaac-mizrahi-married_n_1186082.html/|title=Isaac Mizrahi Married, Shows off Ring on 'Wendy Williams Show' (VIDEO, PHOTOS) |publisher=Huffington Post |date=2012-01-05 |accessdate=2016-03-12}}</ref>\n*[[Michael Kors]], American sportswear fashion designer.<ref name=\"book2\">{{cite book|last=Rappaport|first=Jill|authorlink=|title=Mazel Tov: Celebrities' Bar and Bat Mitzvah Memories|publisher=Simon & Schuster|date=November 2007|location=|pages=|url=https://archive.org/details/mazeltovcelebrit00rapp|isbn=978-0-7432-8787-6|url-access=registration}}</ref><ref name=advocate>{{cite news |title=Working the runway: out designer Michael Kors tells it like it is to would-be fashionistas on Bravo's Project Runway |url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m1589/is_2005_Feb_1/ai_n9487809 |work=The Advocate |date=2005-02-01 |first=Richard |last=Andreoli |accessdate=2007-06-20 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071109211930/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m1589/is_2005_Feb_1/ai_n9487809 <!-- Bot retrieved archive --> |archivedate = 2007-11-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.interviewmagazine.com/fashion/michael-kors|title=Michael Kors|wor